Napoli coach Gennaro Gattuso believes his struggles with an eye disease has had an impact on the team who extended their winless run in Serie A to three games with a 1-1 draw against Torino on Wednesday.
"For a month now there have been rumours that I am dying, but don't worry, I am not dying," said the 42-year-old former World Cup winner.



